{
  "stem": "16345.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father was a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I guess that sort of interfered with his religious life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because according to the very religious Jews, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the state of Israel was not supposed to come into being until the Messiah arrived.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Messiah hadn't arrived at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my parents both believed that the Jews ought to have a homeland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when I was six years old, after that pogrom, we tried to emigrate to Palestine at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they wanted to bring most of their savings, their money with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At the time, the British made up rules about what you can bring into Palestine and what you can't.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of the rules was that there was a limited amount of money you could bring in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my parents decided they-- they didn't want to go without any money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they were killed with their money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were-- they were talking about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one of the pictures that I have left of my father was when he was on Theodor Herzl's grave in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he was a young man, about 19, he went to Vienna and had his picture taken on Herzl's grave.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, most-- mostly everybody attended synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, for instance, my grandfather would attend synagogue, one of the stiebels, just about every day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, for instance, my parents would go to the synagogue only on-- on Shabbos, on the Sabbath, and on the-- on the holidays.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a-- I was a fairly precocious child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I learned not only the Bible, but also the Talmud.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the time I was five years old, I was studying that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
